table concurrent_futures_extra2431.ThreadPoolExecutor_async_iter_protocol:
  description: "concurrent.futures.ThreadPoolExecutor __aiter__ and __anext__ dict-presence checks — ThreadPoolExecutor is a concrete executor using thread workers; no async iteration protocol is defined in its __dict__"
